 on Mr Connollys reply Ssnce wht a person says in papers tiled in an action in court cannot be prosecuted as slander or libel said vfr Connolly the Comptroller hides behind this protection After explaining in detail the con tracts for paving material to which the Comptroller took exception Mr Connolly offered various reasons for the Comptroller hostility toward him among them being the fact he said that some of his friends in Queens had suggested hisConnollysname for the Comptrollership at the coming ttv election On one occasion ONeil the Comp trollers confidential agent and cam paign manager said the Borough President met me upon the street and chided me at having"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-07-14T20:56:36.252Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2009_2010", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-3"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83030214/1921-03-24/ed-1/?sp=7", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_fogler_ver01:data:sn83030214:00206532610:1921032401:0661/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=264&w=209", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_fogler_ver01:data:sn83030214:00206532610:1921032401:0661/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=528&w=419", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_fogler_ver01:data:sn83030214:00206532610:1921032401:0661/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1056&w=839", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_fogler_ver01/data/sn83030214/00206532610/1921032401/0661.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["new york city", "new york", "united states", "new york county"], "location_city": ["new york"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["new york"], "location_state": ["new york"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], 